Text: WHAT A CRAPPY ENDING! i cant believe i gotta wait till september next year to see how this turns out...this ending sucked balls

Don't spoil it jimmy!  I know it wasn't the ending we wanted, but just wait until next season, I have a feeling it's going to be a great one.  We still have 2 more episodes of Dexter until next Sept. too, so enjoy that while ya can as well.
